      "title": "Conference Management System",
      "description": "Built a Spring Boot REST API platform backed by MySQL and Hibernate/JPA to manage paper submissions, user registrations, and event notifications for 150+ users, with Maven for dependency management and Git for version control.\nImplemented Spring Security role-based access control for multiple user types (authors, reviewers, admins) and automated notification workflows using event-driven triggers, reducing administrative workload by 40%.\nOptimized SQL queries and connection pooling, achieving a measurable reduction in average server response time under concurrent load and improving system scalability for hybrid conference setups.",
